beats.description:
Beats Landing is a mobile-first product page built with TypeScript and pure CSS.

Beats Landing is a minimalist product landing page designed with a mobile-first approach for showcasing audio products. The project stands out with a balanced stack of TypeScript (47%) and pure CSS (51%), demonstrating the ability to build modern websites without styling frameworks, with a focus on performance and code clarity.

Implemented functionality:

Mobile-First Design Philosophy:
- responsive layout optimized primarily for smartphones;
- smooth scaling to tablet and desktop without quality loss;
- optimized touch targets for mobile devices;
